snippet.textDisplay: Absolutely amazing, one of my most favorite song of Coke studio's season 9 after Noori's "Paar chana de". Coke studio never fails to amaze us. On the other hand, the love Indian people has for either Pakistani music or Pakistanis (I hope so it's the second one) gave me this new vision for foreseeing them as very nice people as they are way too kind. It's quite nice seeing music uniting the people of the two countries.
